p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">11</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">)术中发现病变为恶性，需改变术式，术后放化疗；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">12</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">)术后发现肿瘤已广泛转移而无法手术切除；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">13</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术中发现新病变需改变术式或扩大手术范围；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">14</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术中由于输卵管与周围组织粘连紧密或损伤严重无法吻合；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">15</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）肌瘤或腺肌瘤剔除困难或剔除过程中因出血多需输血，必要时切除子宫；子宫小肌瘤剥除不净可能，术后子宫肌瘤复发可能；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">16</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）囊肿剥除困难需切除患侧附件；囊肿扭转复位后因血栓脱落栓塞至身体其他器官致肺血栓、脑栓塞等以及相应后果，重者危及生命，必要时需切除患侧附件</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">17</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）附件囊肿扭转坏死严重需切除患侧附件，术后出现卵巢去势综合症，术后生育能力下降；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">18</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）异位妊娠行保留输卵管手术术中应用化疗药物，可能出现肝肾功能损伤、造血功能障碍等不良反应；术中发现患侧输卵管破坏严重无法保留需切除输卵管；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">19</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术后持续异位妊娠、重复性异位妊娠，需二次手术或术后采用化疗等药物；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">20</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术中因</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">CO2</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">气腹综合症、组织气肿、气体栓塞；术后电解质紊乱、肺气肿、</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">DIC</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">、凝血功能障碍；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">21</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）宫腔镜术中急性肺水肿、心衰、溶血、脑水肿、甚至死亡等，水中毒致严重低钠血症，子宫穿孔、宫腔感染；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">22</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）伤口并发症：出血、血肿、感染、裂开、不愈合，及手术并发症，如直肠阴道瘘、膀胱阴道瘘、输尿管及膀胱损伤、肠损伤、血管损伤等；切口疝形成，或因特殊体位致神经损伤；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">23</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术后静脉血栓、脂肪、癌组织栓塞形成，严重者可导致昏迷及呼吸衰竭，危及生命；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">24</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）阴道手术术后阴道缩短或瘢痕形成影响性生活；术后阴道脱垂复发可能，需手术治疗；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">25</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术后肠粘连、肠梗阻、膀胱功能障碍及盆腔淋巴囊肿形成，必要时手术治疗；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">26</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术后生育几率降低；手术不能完全满足妊娠需要；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">27</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）各种医疗保险患者术中使用薇乔线、医用几丁糖、超声刀等，费用自付；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">28</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">)除上述情况外，尚有可能发生的其他并发症或者需要提前请患者及家属特别注意的其他事项，如：</span><input name="新增的输入域" border-style="1" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">  </span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> </span></input><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">4</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.我理解如果我患有高血压、心脏病、糖尿病、肝肾功能不全、静脉血栓等疾病或者有吸烟史，以上这些风险可能会加大，或者在术中或术后出现相关的病情加重或心脑血管意外，甚至死亡。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">5</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.我理解术后如果我的体位不当或不遵医嘱，可能影响手术效果。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontbold="1" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">特殊风险或主要高危因素</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    我理解根据我个人的病情，我可能出现未包括在上述所交待并发症以外的风险：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><input name="新增的输入域" operatercreater="0" border-style="1" forecolor="#000000"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">                                                                                 </span></input><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">一旦发生上述风险和意外，医生会采取积极应对措施。</span><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="C57F6121342" width="660" operatercreater="0"><cell id="C57F6121343" width="660" operatercreater="0"><span fontbold="1" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">患者知情选择</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">   </span><span fontsize="16" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">·</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">我的医生已经告知我将要进行的手术方式、此次手术及术后可能发生的并发症和风险、      可能存在的其它治疗方法并且解答了我关于此次手术的相关问题。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">   </span><span fontsize="16" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">·</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">我同意在手术中医生可以根据我的病情对预定的手术方式做出调整。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">   </span><span fontsize="16" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">·</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">我理解我的手术需要多位医生共同进行。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">   </span><span fontsize="16" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">·</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">我并未得到手术百分之百成功的许诺。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">   </span><span fontsize="16" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">·</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">我授权医师对手术切除的病变器官、组织或标本进行处置，包括病理学检查、细胞学检      查和医疗废物处理等。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  	</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">患者签名</span><span forecolor="#000000" fontunderline="1" operatercreater="0">                                 </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">        签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">如果患者无法签署知情同意书，请其授权的亲属在此签名：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">患者授权亲属签名</span><span forecolor="#000000" fontunderline="1" operatercreater="0">          </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> 与患者关系</span><span forecolor="#000000" fontunderline="1" operatercreater="0">          </span><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">  签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="C57F6121347" width="660" operatercreater="0"><cell id="C57F6121348" width="660" operatercreater="0"><span fontbold="1" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">医生陈述</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    我已经告知患者将要进行的手术方式、此次手术及术后可能发生的并发症和风险、可能存在的其它治疗方法并且解答了患者关于此次手术的相关问题。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">医师签名</span><input name="医师签名" operatercreater="0"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">     </span></input><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">                          签名日期</span><input name="日期" operatercreater="0"><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">      年   月   日</span></input><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row></table><p operatercreater="0" /></body></emrtextdoc></body></emrtextdoc>